\v 19 Pahrien, k…ôn n…®kik otagien m…®n m…ôto-inu ek…®tun m…ôm…ô e noa n…ôfak…ôn r…ôhat…ômat, ne nasitu…ôn r…ôha Narm…®n r…ôha Iesu Kristo, in otosmeg…ôh io e n…ôrat…ôn u,\x - \xo 1:19 \xt 2 Kor 1:11 \x*
\v 20 tahmen …ôm m…ôm…ô iakolkeike p…®k k…ôn mat…ôl…ôh…ôu-p…ôn r…ôhak n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn m…ôm…ô oesol…ôn nat kit it…ôm otol aul…®s io e n…®gan…ômt…® Uhg…®n. M…ôto roiu ne nian rafin, n…®kik t…ôskas…®k m…ôm…ô ok…ôm…ô iat…ômeg…ôh o ek…®m…®s, m…ôto iat…®siai-in Kristo e n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôhak.
\v 21 Tol n…ôhlan m…ôto-inu n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôhak in Kristo …ôm, k…ôn ok…ôm…ô ek…®m…®s, in nat t…ôw…®r tapr…ôk…®s.\x - \xo 1:21 \xt Kal 2:20 \x*
\v 22 Ok…ôm…ô iat…ômeg…ôh …ôh, in t…ôw…®r o nol…ôn w…ôk m…ôs…®n m…®n r…ôha Uhg…®n e n…ôtueint…ôn. ?K…ôn ek…®t…ôpun it…ôm p…ôhru…ôn? !I…ôk…ôruru!
\v 23 Roiu …ôh suat…®p k…ôiu katu…ôm…ôhl aup…ôn in io, m…ôto iakolkeike ilau k…ôr…ôn. Iakolkeike p…®k m…ôm…ô iakap…ôs nat…®g…ôn ik…®n-u muw…®n m…ôplan Kristo it…ôm in t…ôw…®r ag…®n mapr…ôk…®s-in nat…®g…ôn u ik…®n-u.\x - \xo 1:23 \xt 2 Kor 5:8 \x*
