\v 12 R…ôhak net…ômim m…®n it…ôm iakolkeike p…®k, nian em…ôtan kitat min it…ômat, it…ômat n…ômoatol n…ôwiak nian rafin. K…ôn roiu, m…ôto-inu etat…®g is…ôu ot…ômat, it…ômat at…®p n…ôkot…ôk…ôike motalkut …ôskas…®k m…ôm…ô n…ôkoatol n…ôwiak e nat…®mnat m…®n u: m…ôto-inu n…®not…®tun r…ôk…®s nol…ôn …ôh r…ôha Kristo, otalkut …ôskas…®k o n…ôt…ôu-p…ôn…ôn suat…®p r…ôha nosmeg…ôh…ôn. Ot…ôt…ôu-p…ôn suat…®p …ôh e n…®gan…ômt…® Uhg…®n motasi…ôp mot…ôgin.
\v 13 K…ôn ot…ôt…ôu-p…ôn suat…®p …ôh m…ôto-inu Uhg…®n tatol w…ôk e n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôhat…ômat m…ôm…ô on…ôkotolkeike m…ôm…ô n…ôkoatol n…ôwian, k…ôn tatos-ip…®n…ô n…ôsan…ôn…ôn k…ôm it…ômat m…ôm…ô on…ôkotol pahrien n…ôwian.
\p 
\v 14 E nat…®mnat rafin it…ôm n…ôkoatol, sot…ôghat-…ôghat…ôn ron, k…ôn m…ôsot…ôrg…ôh…ôu…ôn ron
\v 15 m…ôm…ô n…ômeg…ôh…ôn r…ôhat…ômat ot…ôtuat…®p w…®r, k…ôn k…ôsehm-p…ôn…ôn n…ôrat…ôn kit lan, k…ôn it…ômat nen…ôt…® Uhg…®n it…ôm nol…ôn eko-eko t…®k…ô et…ômat, it…ôm n…ôkotat…®g e n…ôlug…® net…ôm koteko-eko, iapin…ôp m…®n. K…ôn it…ômat nakot…ôhag-…ôhag tahmen e m…ôhau m…®n e n…ôtueint…ôn
\v 16 it…ôm nakotask…ôl…®m w…®r n…ôghat…ôn e n…ômeg…ôh…ôn. Ken otol nat…®mnat m…®n …ôh rafin m…ôm…ô nian Kristo tatuwa m…®n, k…ôn ekausit ot…ômat, k…ôn oek…®tun m…ôm…ô esaiu …ôpnap…®n…ôn, nahgik t…ôs…®k…ô…ôn o nat …ôpnap…®n …ôm.\x - \xo 2:16 \xt Dan 12:3; Fil 1:10; 1 Tes 2:19 \x*
\v 17 Nol…ôn r…ôhat…ômat r…ôha nahat…ôt…ô…ôn e Uhg…®n tahmen e sakrifais\f + \fr 2:17 \ft Nian tep…ôt net…ôm Isrel koatoh nat meg…ôh m…®n motuwaan e n…®g…ôm …ôp…ôh e Nim…ô R…ôha Uhg…®n m…ôm…ô okot…ôfak. Nian neen koat…ôht…ôg-p…ôn wain o n…ôhau e nat meg…ôh it…ôm n…®g…ôm tatus tahmen e nos-ip…ôn…ôn k…ôm Uhg…®n.\f* kit k…ôm Uhg…®n. Ok…ôm-naka ek…®m…®s, k…ôn muwa mahmen e sakrifais e wain it…ôm kat…ôht…ôg-p…ôn ilau sakrifais r…ôhat…ômat. M…ôto nat …ôpnap…®n …ôm, n…®kik tagien …ôm kitat min it…ômat.
\v 18 K…ôn e nol…ôn kiti…ôh …ôm, n…®kit…ômat t…ôk…ôike magien it…ômat min io.\x - \xo 2:18 \xt Fil 3:1; 4:4 \x*
\s1 Timoti ne Epafrotaetas
\p 
\v 19 Ok…ôm…ô I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô Iesu teg…ôhan-in, iakolkeike m…ôm…ô ekahl-ip…®n…ô Timoti t…®mn…ô m…ôplan it…ômat m…ôm…ô nian iak…ôto namnus…ôn et…ômat, k…ôn io m…®n, n…®kik otagien.
\v 20 Suah kit t…®k…ô m…®n u ik…®n-u it…ôm r…ôhan n…ôt…ôl…®g…ôn tahmen e r…ôha Timoti, it…ôm n…®kin tat…ôht p…®k it…ômat.
\v 21 Net…ôm p…®s…®n p…®s…®n koat…ôt…ôl…®g-in at…®p …ôm w…ôk m…®n r…ôhalat, m…ôsot…ôt…ôl…®g-in…ôn w…ôk r…ôha Iesu Kristo.\x - \xo 2:21 \xt 2 Tim 4:10 \x*
\v 22 M…ôto it…ômat n…ôkot…®tun m…ôm…ô nian rafin tahro nulan Timoti tatol w…ôk r…ôha Uhg…®n, k…ôn r…ôhan w…ôk in t…ôw…®r, k…ôn tahmen e suak…ôku tatol w…ôk ilau r…ôhan tata, in t…ômasitu lak e w…ôk r…ôha namnus…ôn t…ôw…®r.
\v 23 M…ôto-inu o nat …ôh, n…®kik tat…ôht m…ôm…ô nian oek…®tun m…ôm…ô r…ôhak nat…®g…ôn otahro nulan, oekahl-ip…®n…ô u…ôhai …ôm t…®mn…ô mehm it…ômat,
\v 24 k…ôn ekahat…ôt…ô e I…ôr…ôm…ôr…ô m…ôm…ô ot…ôsuw…ôh…ôn io m…®n ek…®mn…ô mehm it…ômat.
\p 
\v 25 M…ôto n…®kik t…ôht m…ôm…ô ek…ôike mahl-ip…®n…ô Epafrotaetas t…®t…ôl…®g-p…®n…ô m…ôplan it…ômat. In piak it…ôm iatuea kiti…ôh matioal w…ôk kiti…ôh, k…ôn matu…ôluag…®n e n…ôluag…®n…ôn kiti…ôh r…ôha Uhg…®n. Aup…ôn n…ômotahl-ipa e n…ôrg…®t…ômat m…ôm…ô otuwa m…ôn-iar…ôp k…ôm io namnus…ôn r…ôhat…ômat, k…ôn m…ôm…ô otasitu lak.\x - \xo 2:25 \xt Fil 4:18 \x*
